Class BaseLayoutBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomscz.afswinx.component.widget.builder.abstraction.BaseLayoutBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayoutBuilder

    public class BaseLayoutBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements LayoutBuilder
    This is base layout builder which can build layout for concrete Layout. It can build layout for field or for class as well.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
    Author:
    Martin Tomasek (martin@toms-cz.com)
